text: aur yadi ve tauraat aur inajeel ko aur jo kuchh unake rab kee or se unakee or utaara gaya hai, use qaayam rakhate, to unhen apane oopar se bhee khaane ko milata aur apane paanv ke neeche se bhee. unamen se ek giroh seedhe maarg par chalanevaala bhee hai, kintu unamen se adhikatar aise hai ki jo bhee karate hai bura hota hai
